---
// src/components/home/SoftCTA.astro
// Low-pressure call-to-action for visitors not ready to commit.
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-28 text-center" aria-label="Get in touch">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
    <h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.5rem)] text-brand-text leading-tight mb-4 reveal">
      Not Sure Where to Start?
    </h2>

    <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8 reveal reveal-d1">
      We'll tell you what's working, what's not, and what would actually move the needle — no pitch, no pressure. Just honest advice from someone who builds this stuff every day.
    </p>

    <a
      href="/contact"
      class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border border-brand-border hover:border-brand-dim text-brand-muted hover:text-brand-text font-semibold text-[0.95rem] rounded-xl transition-all reveal reveal-d2"
    >
      Ask Us Anything
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
